name: startup
description: **FeastFinder:** the go-to app for college students seeking free or low-cost food events on campus. This platform connects students with up-to-date information on where to find free meals, snacks, and food-related gatherings. Whether it's a service activity, a guest lecture, or a social event, if there's free food, it's on FeastFinder. Save money, discover new events, and enjoy the campus life to its fullest!
